gb(221, 57, 46); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;04&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(221, 57, 46); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(221, 57, 46);\">‖ 陆地萌宠“新”世界</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 57, 46);\">（部分需自费，以现场收费为准）</span></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 57, 46);\">No.1 萌宠乐园</span></strong></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">这里有鸵鸟、骆驼、小鹿等超多萌宠等你来发现哦~</span></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hupovip.cn//ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20191030/1572429031388070067.jpg?x-oss-process=style/image-zip\" title=\"1391572402628_.pic_hd\" alt=\"1391572402628_.pic_hd.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hupovip.cn//ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20200312/1583998692514004234.jpg?x-oss-process=style/image-zip\" title=\"萌宠乐园3\" alt=\"萌宠乐园3.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hupovip.cn//ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20200312/1583998738833068474.jpg?x-oss-process=style/image-zip\" title=\"n191018_9715\" alt=\"n191018_9715.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hupovip.cn//ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20191030/1572429040453064837.jpg?x-oss-process=style/image-zip\" title=\"1401572402632_.pic_hd\" alt=\"1401572402632_.pic_hd.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hupovip.cn//ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20191030/1572429044663045483.jpg?x-oss-process=style/image-zip\" title=\"981572402440_.pic_hd\" alt=\"981572402440_.pic_hd.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 57, 46);\"><strong>No.2&nbsp;动物运动会</strong></span></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">动物运动会，是指由小朋友亲自参与，与动物互动比赛，如山羊障碍赛、小猪赛跑、小狗逃生等等，结伴出战，趣味横生……</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hupovip.cn//ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20191030/1572429063253043529.jpg?x-oss-process=style/image-zip\" title=\"1371572402621_.pic_hd\" alt=\"1371572402621_.pic_hd.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hupovip.cn//ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20191030/1572429067128042762.jpg?x-oss-process=style/image-zip\" title=\"1361572402618_.pic_hd\" alt=\"1361572402618_.pic_hd.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 57, 46);\"><strong>No.3&nbsp;松鼠部落岛</strong></span></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">金花松鼠、大魔王松鼠、欧洲红腹松鼠、黄山松鼠……穿越松鼠部落岛，乖巧灵活，喜欢吃瓜子和花生，树林之间，不停穿梭，嬉戏打闹……下设座位，欢迎围观~</span></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hupovip.cn//ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20190924/1569289863089032772.jpg?x-oss-process=style/image-zip\" title=\"c813db7c13f857fe6544597c1fdb76b6\" alt=\"c813db7c13f857fe6544597c1fdb76b6.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(221, 57, 46); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>05&nbsp;</strong><strong>‖ 科普放映室&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></span></span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">萌宠新世界三大升级之一的科普研学，也是我们重点推荐的项目之一，在这儿休憩观影，了解动物常识与基本知识，有助于小朋友们对大自然的敬畏与了解，增长学识，实物与教学相结合……</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hupovip.cn//ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20190924/1569289912899092075.jpg?x-oss-process=style/image-zip\" style=\"\" title=\"微信图片_20190924095458\"/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hupovip.cn//ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20190924/1569289913048073210.jpg?x-oss-process=style/image-zip\" style=\"\" title=\"微信图片_20190923191441\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(221, 57, 46); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>06&nbsp;</strong><strong>‖ 百鸟林奇幻岛&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong style=\"text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(221, 57, 46); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><br/></strong></span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">美丽的孔雀正在湖里倒影着自己美丽的尾翼，八哥、鹦鹉、小鹌鹑，各种鸟儿们欢歌畅语，一片蝉鸣鸟叫，真是热闹，从百鸟林奇幻岛穿越出去更有新大陆等你去欣赏……</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hupovip.cn//ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20191030/1572431926714023683.jpg?x-oss-process=style/image-zip\" title=\"1191572402553_.pic_hd\" alt=\"1191572402553_.pic_hd.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(221, 57, 46); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>07&nbsp;</strong><strong>‖ 杰克逊马场&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">异域风情，西部牛仔，欧洲进口矮种马，驯养中马，带你领略不一样的驾驭乐趣，小朋友们更有专属的矮种马可以体验，与爸爸妈妈并驾齐驱，体验西部牛仔的潇洒乐趣……</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hupovip.cn//ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20190924/1569290056013081269.jpg?x-oss-process=style/image-zip\" title=\"微信图片_20190924095634\" alt=\"微信图片_20190924095634.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(221, 57, 46); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>08&nbsp;</strong><strong>‖ 蛋窝之家科普园&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">作为动物科普重要组成板块之一的蛋窝之家，以蛋的形式展现各种恐龙的世界，与各种恐龙的科普文化知识，在这里我们特意设计制作了各种蛋的模型与恐龙展示……开启自学模式吧，小伙伴们！</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hupovip.cn//ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20190924/1569290343425067913.jpg?x-oss-process=style/image-zip\" title=\"微信图片_20190924095822\" alt=\"微信图片_20190924095822.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">超多精彩，尽在音乐百花谷！</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">快带上你的家人一起来玩吧！</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hupovip.cn/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20180813/1534170160293058234.png?x-oss-process=image/format,jpg/quality,q_60/resize,w_750\" title=\"交通路线\" alt=\"交通路线.png\" style=\"width: 400px;\"/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; white-space: normal;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 57, 46);\">▼自驾</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">导航搜索：四川省成都市新都区叠秀路962号音乐百花谷内</span></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hupovip.cn/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20180619/1529378678658012424.png?x-oss-process=image/format,jpg/quality,q_60/resize,w_750\" title=\"温馨提示\" alt=\"温馨提示.png\" style=\"width: 400px;\"/><br/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">客服咨询：请直接点击左下角客服图标进行咨询。</span></p><p><br/></p>',
